<key>GAMETXT_PROLOGUE1</key>
<string>IN THE SULTAN’S ABSENCE, THE GRAND VIZIER\nJAFFAR RULES WITH AN IRON FIST OF TYRANNY.\n\nONLY ONE OBSTACLE REMAINS BETWEEN JAFFAR\nAND THE THRONE:\n\nTHE SULTAN’S BEAUTIFUL\nYOUNG DAUGHTER. . . \n\n</string>
#
<key>GAME_TXT_EPILOGUE</key>
<string>THE TYRANT JAFFAR LIES DEAD,\nHIS POWER SHATTERED.\n\n THROUGHOUT THE LAND, THE PEOPLE OF PERSIA\nHAILTHEIR PRINCESS AND\nTHE BRAVE YOUTH WHO SAVED HER \nFROM THE FORCES OF DARKNESS. \n\nNO LONGER A STRANGER,\nHE SHALL FROM THIS DAY FORTH BE KNOWN AS. . . \n\n PRINCE OF PERSIA.</string>
#
<key>GAME_TXT_PROLOGUE2</key>
<string>ONLY YOU CAN SAVE THE SULTAN'S\n DAUGHTER FROM JAFFAR\nAND FREE THE LAND FROM HIS REIGN OF TYRANNY.\n\nYOU WILL HAVE TO ESCAPE FROM PRISON\nAND FIND YOUR WAY THROUGH THE PALACE\nTO SAVE YOUR BELOVED PRINCESS BEFORE\nTHE LAST SANDS IN THE HOURGLASS RUN OUT.\n\nMANY TRAPS AND GUARDS AWAIT\nYOU IN THE DUNGEON.\n\nYOU MUST OVERCOME THESE PERILS, FIGHT\nYOUR WAY UP TO THE HIGHEST TOWER\nWHERE THE PRINCESS IS BEING\nHELD CAPTIVE AND PUT AN END TO\n JAFFAR'S EVIL PLAN.</string>
#
<key>GAME_TXT_FINISH</key>
<string>CONGRATULATIONS!\nYOU HAVE SUCCESSFULLY COMPLETED\nPRINCE OF PERSIA CLASSIC HD.</string>
#
<key>GAME_TXT_CSTXT</key>
<string>MEANWHILE. . . </string>
#
<key>STANDBY_SCREEN</key>
<string>TAP THE SCREEN TO CONTINUE</string>
#
<key>GAME_OVER</key>
<string>GAME OVER</string>
#
<key>BUY_FULL</key>
<string>GET FULL GAME NOW</string>
