<key>TUTORIAL_01_MOVE</key>
<string>Slide # to walk or run in that direction. </string>
#
<key>TUTORIAL_02_CROUCH</key>
<string>Tap # to crouch on the spot.</string>
#
<key>TUTORIAL_03_DOWN</key>
<string>Tap and hold # to descend a floor. </string>
#
<key>TUTORIAL_04_JUMP</key>
<string>Tap # to jump on the spot or grab a ledge to avoid a fall.</string>
#
<key>TUTORIAL_05_CLIMB</key>
<string>Hold # to climb the ledge.</string>
#
<key>TUTORIAL_06_FALL</key>
<string>If you fall, move # in the opposite direction to hold onto a ledge. </string>
#
<key>TUTORIAL_07_GRAB</key>
<string>Tap # to pick up objects.</string>
#
<key>TUTORIAL_08_SPIKES</key>
<string>You can jump over or walk slowly through the spikes.</string>
#
<key>TUTORIAL_09_SLICER</key>
<string>Timing is of the essence to cross the Slicer.</string>
#
<key>TUTORIAL_10_BUTTON</key>
<string>Find the right button to open the gate. </string>
#
<key>TUTORIAL_11_FALSEBTN</key>
<string>Some buttons are traps. Avoid interacting with them.</string>
#
<key>TUTORIAL_12_ATTACK</key>
<string>Tap # to swing the sword.</string>
#
<key>TUTORIAL_13_DEFEND</key>
<string>Hold # to go on the defensive.</string>
#
<key>TUTORIAL_14_PARRY</key>
<string>Tap # to avoid enemy attack.</string>
#
<key>TUTORIAL_15_COMBAT</key>
<string>Timing your actions is absolutely essential to survive in combat.</string>
#
<key>TIPS_1</key>
<string>Tap DEFEND to avoid enemy attack and then \nrapidly tap ATTACK To perform a fast counter-attack.</string>
#
<key>TIPS_2</key>
<string>Walk, don't run! \nWalking over spike traps will avoid a painful situation.</string>
#
<key>TIPS_3</key>
<string>Tap DEFEND to avoid enemy counter-attacks.</string>
#
<key>TIPS_4</key>
<string>You won't win this fight without a weapon. Try to find another way.</string>
#
<key>TIPS_5</key>
<string>Tap JUMP to grab a ledge. Keep it tapped to climb.</string>
#
<key>TIPS_6</key>
<string>Once you have grabbed the ledge, \ntap JUMP once to climb up. </string>
#
<key>TIPS_7</key>
<string>Tap JUMP while running to perform a Long Jump.</string>
#
<key>TIPS_8</key>
<string>The Butterfly may help you find the way out.</string>
#
<key>TIPS_9</key>
<string>The Dark Prince cannot be defeated by ordinary means.</string>
#
<key>TIPS_10</key>
<string>Timing And Patience are virtues: \nThey are your keys to surviving the slicers.</string>
#
<key>TIPS_11</key>
<string>Find loose tiles by the dust stirred up when \nyou jump near to them.</string>
#
<key>TIPS_12</key>
<string>You can safely walk through or jump over spike traps.</string>
#
<key>TIPS_13</key>
<string>Tap CROUCH while running to dive.</string>
#
<key>TIPS_14</key>
<string>Loose Tiles Fall when walked on or hit from below.</string>
#
<key>TIPS_15</key>
<string>Crouch or Roll to cross closing gates.</string>
#
<key>TIPS_16</key>
<string>Slide MOVEMENT BUTTON back while jumping \nto perform a back flip.</string>
#
<key>TIPS_17</key>
<string>You can jump onto walls to propel yourself and climb faster.</string>
#
<key>TIPS_18</key>
<string>Share your progress with your friends on facebook and via mail.</string>
#
<key>TIPS_19</key>
<string>Tap JUMP while walking to JUMP FORWARD</string>
#
<key>TIPS_20</key>
<string>You can modify the controls layout from the in-game menu.</string>
#
