<key>LITE_TEXT</key>
<string>Complete all 14 levels to save the princess.Face the daunting guards and the evil jaffar. Prove your mettle with additional game modes.Uncover dark secrets as you progress.Share your adventure with friends on facebook. Unlock Achievements to recognize your skill Earn a place on the Leaderboards for glory!Your destiny awaits you, stranger… You are the Princess’s only hope. </string>
